**Description**:
Button like triggered |scroll left|right| actions momentary scrolling to ends;

**Steps to reproduce**:
1. open|create file with at least 1 line longer than editor's window;
2. trigger horizontal scrolling by button like controller (tilt wheel for example);

**Additional information**:
if triggering vertical scrolling actions on buttons they working fine;

